Package com.poesys.ms.pk

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IPrimaryKey
    A generic interface for primary key data transfer objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractPrimaryKey
    An abstract implementation of the IPrimaryKey interface that implements elements shared between all the primary key classes.
    AssociationPrimaryKey
    A concrete implementation of the IPrimaryKey interface that represents an association primary key.
    AssociationPrimaryKeyTest
    Tests the AssociationPrimaryKey messaging DTO class
    CompositePrimaryKey
    An implementation of the IPrimaryKey interface that represents a composite primary key.
    CompositePrimaryKeyTest
    Tests the CompositePrimaryKey messaging DTO class
    GuidPrimaryKey
    Implements the IPrimaryKey interface for a key constructed from a single UUID value.
    GuidPrimaryKeyTest
    Tests the GuidPrimaryKey messaging DTO
    IdentityPrimaryKey
    Implements the identity primary key (a generated integer value key).
    IdentityPrimaryKeyTest
    Tests the IdentityPrimaryKey messaging DTO
    NaturalPrimaryKey
    Implements the IPrimaryKey interface with a list of single-valued columns.
    NaturalPrimaryKeyTest
    Tests the NaturalPrimaryKey messaging DTO class
    SequencePrimaryKey
    Implements the sequence primary key (a generated integer value)
    SequencePrimaryKeyTest
    Tests the SequencePrimaryKey messaging DTO
